flowchart TD
  Request[Stage requests integration] --> Queue[Serialized merge queue]
  Queue --> Lock[Acquire single dev/main integration lock]
  Lock --> Preflight{Preflight gates pass}

  Preflight -->|no| Blocked[Blocked with exact failed gate]
  Preflight -->|yes| FreshBase{Branch fresh against dev/main}
  FreshBase -->|no| Rebase[Deterministic rebase or merge base refresh]
  Rebase --> ConflictCheck{Conflicts}
  FreshBase -->|yes| ConflictCheck
  ConflictCheck -->|yes| ConflictBlocked[Blocked with conflict file list]
  ConflictCheck -->|no| Merge[Integrate branch into dev/main]
  Merge --> Validate[Run integration tests and SDD doctor]
  Validate --> ValidationResult{Validation passes}
  ValidationResult -->|no| RollBack[Abort integration and preserve evidence]
  ValidationResult -->|yes| Record[Record merge commit, logs, tests, doctor output]
  Record --> Ready[Mark ready for PROD promotion]

  Blocked --> Remediate[Fix in original stage worktree]
  ConflictBlocked --> Remediate
  RollBack --> Remediate
  Remediate --> Request

